<td colspan="2" class="summary" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background-color: lightsteelblue">King David Hotel Bombing</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/File:King_david_hotel_bombing1.jpg" class="image" title="King david hotel bombing1.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/83/King_david_hotel_bombing1.jpg" width="250" height="376" border="0" /></a><br />
