1_3-26" title=""><sup><i><b>aa</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-tclarke81_3-27" title=""><sup><i><b>ab</b></i></sup></a> Thurston Clarke, <i>By Blood and Fire</i>, G. P. Puttnam's Sons, New York, 1981</li>
